<P>
   FBN-JETS-PARCELLS (Undated) _ Coach Bill Parcells is used to
surpassing expectations when it comes to pulling a football team
from the ashes. He did it with the New York Giants; he did it with
the New England Patriots earlier this decade. But nothing in
Parcells' resume _ perhaps in no professional coaching resume _
compares with what Parcells has accomplished with the Jets. By Mike
Freeman. With photos.
</P>
