<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-16 12:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5169 &Cx1f; var-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-IMPEACH-HOWLONG?-REVI     01-16 0529
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-IMPEACH-HOWLONG?-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
 
WASHINGTON: be deconstructed. 
<TEXT>
