   ATLANTA _
</P>
<P>
   _ Team: Detroit
</P>
<P>
   _ Update: Ranks 11th on the all-time goal-scoring list with 581.
Will start at center for North America in next Sunday's All-Star
Game in Tampa.
</P>
<P>
   _ On how he would grade Detroit's first half: ``I guess a `C.'
It's been a struggle. We've had a tough time in various games to
really come in with a lot of energy, a lot of excitement and
enthusiasm necessary to win games against some teams who are really
playing hard and playing well. Our play as an entire team
defensively, we've just allowed far too many goals to win games. As
a team we're a lot sloppier.''
</P>
