   _ On speculation of the Wings' Stanley Cup hangover: ``I don't
know if that is a term I'd use. It's not like we're sitting around
and said, 'Well, we'll kind of coast along the first half of the
year and get it going in the second half and be ready by playoff
time.' But there is no question we have had a tough time. I think
as long as we keep grinding along, we'll get it back.''
</P>
<P>
