<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Austin's biggest party . . . where and how to join in
 &HT;    By Michele Chan Santos
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   AUSTIN, Texas _ Gov. George W. Bush will be inaugurated Tuesday
